pen in `ros/CMakeLists.txt` and are received in `ros/atlas_msgs/CMakeLists.txt`.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>In our efforts to call out to rosbuild via <code>ExternalProject_Add()</code>, we added a bunch of environment variable setting.  Then we figured out that we were missing an override of <code>dh_auto_build</code> in the debian <code>rules</code> file.  We should go back and audit the environment variable settings, with the goal of reducing them to the minimum set.</p>\n<p>The settings in questions happen in <code>ros/CMakeLists.txt</code> and are received in <code>ros/atlas_msgs/CMakeLists.txt</code>.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Brian Gerkey", "uuid": "{3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9/5fa9ec73-0fec-4860-a202-e34ae23b6a12/128"}}, "nickname": "Brian Gerkey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9"}, "state": "wontfix", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-01-28T20:22:48.620030+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2013-04-11T03:00:49.299365+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 102}